Only murder, wanted and unexplained deaths..real crime stuff.
The quality is very poor. Old vhs tapes which has been compressed into small file size. Typical vhs noise on most.

Time: About 6 hours

How to burn:
I have chosen .iso file.
If you use ImgBurn: WRITE IMAGE FILE TO DISC
I tested it at 6x write speed and it worked perfectly...
Remember to keep the .iso file on your pc so you can seed.

Disc 14
- Jacqueline Dowaliby - Young girl is murdered and her adopted father was convicted of the crime. Later exonerated. Looking for her killer.
- Lyle Moody is wanted for shooting and injuring two cops. He's on the run.
- Unidentified man in coma - Was involved in an accident. Police are trying to find his family and his identity.
- Lawrence Harding Jr. was abducted as an infant. His brother is searching for him.
- Special Alert: Tyrone Thiess is wanted for a triple murder.
- Special Alert: Shannon Smith is wanted for the rape of underage girls.
- Wallace Thrasher is an international drug runner. His wife claims he died in a plane crash but authorities think he is still alive.
- Kelly Finnigan is a conwoman wanted for robbing men with her "red wine con".
- Randolph Dial is accused of breaking out of prison and kidnapping the Deputy Warden's wife. Police are searching for both of them.
- Neal & Terri Gott are being sought by police for drug dealing.
- Robert Leeds is wanted for art theft. RS profiles other famous works of art that have been stolen.
- "Thumper" - Outlaw biker is wanted for making meth labs.
- Tina Resch claims to have telekinetic powers and that things move mysteriously when she's around.
- Joseph Prushanowski - Jewish community leader who is wanted for international bank fraud.
- John Grundhofer is abducted by an inept kidnapper. He later escapes and police are searching for his abductor.
- Brian Brophill is wanted for narcotics smuggling and drug dealing.
- Zip Gun Bomber has been sending bombs through the mail. One person has died and others wounded. Searching for who is responsible.
- Mollie Jordan's house was set on fire, killing several of her grandchildren inside. Police are searching for the arsonist.
- Noreen Renier is a psychic who is profiled.
- Kay Beeman, prison guard, is wanted for helping two inmates escape one of whom she was romantically involved with.
- Reverse Sting Operation - Authorities work to bust several individuals accused of bribing police officers.
- Final Appeal: Bird Road Rapist. Luis Diaz was convicted of rapes that occurred in the Florida area but several people believe he is innocent.
- McDonald's Shooting - Police are searching for Michael Anthony Star who they believed robbed a McDonalds in Virginia shooting and maming the asst. manager.
- Coma victim "John" has been unresponsive for 7 months following being hit by a motorcycle while walking. They are looking for his identity and his family.
- Psychic surgery - Gary Magnou is wanted for conning many people out of money with his phony surgery claims.
- Clifford Sherwood was 9 years old when he went missing while on his way to school in 1954. Did he run away or meet with foul play?
- Jim Fontes, police officer, is searching for his two sons whom his ex-wife abducted.
- Lynn Amos is found barely alive in her burning bed. She later died. Was it a random act of violence or connected to her job?
- Amy Bradley disappears while vacationing with her family on a cruise ship.
- Carl & Mary Denny are wanted for insurance fraud concerning a boat.
- Kristi Lee is found dead in her apartment. Her in-laws are not cooperating with the investigation and are considered suspects.
- Randal Utterback escaped from prison where he was being held for kidnapping his ex-girlfriend. He is on the run and police are searching for him.
- Audrey Moate & Thomas Houtard were lovers. Thomas was found near a lovers lane murdered but Audrey was gone and has never been seen since. Did she meet with foul play as well?
- Seattle arsonist is blamed for a rash of extremely intense fires that have killed 1 firefighter and cost millions.
- Jim Boomgarden keeps running into strangers who claim they know him. He recently found out he has a twin brother as well as a sister he is searching for.
- Selena Edon was badly injured in a motorcycle accident leaving her with some confusion. She has since disappeared.
